latestIgtvVideos.title: Black smokey date night glam 🍇
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Quick black smokey in a few steps -

Step 1 - using a black kajal pencil @Bobbi brownindia or your @maybelline gel pot and smudge it over your lid. Let it transition from dark medium to light , the darkest colour being close to the eyelash line

Step 2 - use a soft brown crease colour from the  @hudabeauty rose gold palette and diffuse the colours using the @maccosmeticsindia blending brush 
Step 3 - add a black eyeshadow on top. I love the @maccosmeticsindia carbon black with a lil glitter in it 🌟

Step 4 - line the Lower water line to balance the smokey effect on the eye 
@urbandecaycosmetics 
Step 5 - Add a doze of shimmer on the inner corner of the eye to enhance the glamour @beccacosmetics 
How simple was that ? ❤️❤️❤️ #blacksmokeyeye #datenightglam #blushloungebysneha #blushlookbook
